name: God’s Got An Army
chorusText:
God’s got an army(G)
God’s got an army that’s marching through this land.
Deliverance is their songwith healing in their hands
Everlasting joy and gladness in their hearts
and in this army, I’ve got a part

It’s the Holy Ghost and power
And it’s keeping me alive.
Keeping me alive, keeping me alive
It’s the Holy Ghost and power
and it’s keeping me alive
Jesus is keeping me alive.

     God’s not dead … no!He’s alive    x3
I feel Him in my hands
I feel Himin my feet
I feel Him in my heart
I feel it all over me!
